{"tid":1524042,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"致愛香港既真香港人 成立自衛隊","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T13:32:32.000Z","uid":208536,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"18ef41e5e471c84da8c59a48ff8c281f540677c6","tid":1524042,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:34:11.000Z","msg":"之前標題開得唔夠靚<br />\n<br />\n唔好再同我講對準主線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1523882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1523882</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n打狗依啲一定要做<br />\n但我知好多人未有心理準備<br />\n未有經驗<br />\n你可以唔夠膽做絕育流浪狗<br />\n<br />\n依家有一個最好既機會<br />\n就係立成自衛隊 去保持社會安穩<br />\n黑社會人人得而誅之<br />\n訓練自己 <br />\n<br />\n唔好再講咩focus主線<br />\n支線會阻礙主線<br />\n依家係班撚屌黑社會 收哂錢打人<br />\n覺得我地唔敢還拖<br />\n發洩完仲有錢收<br />\n我依家話俾你班廢撚元朗牛屎佬 北角福建佬聽<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要你地有錢無仲享</span></span><br />\n<br />\n召集所有發夢當日遲到 或者唔得閒無到既手足<br />\n跟隊完場之後入元朗同北角<br />\n保護手足平安番屋企<br />\n<br />\n另外大西北手足同港島手足 希望成立自衛隊<br />\n打殘黑社會 <br />\n港島已有小量手足準備加入<br />\n<br />\n首先 黑社會依啲社會垃圾一早應該被清算<br />\n打殘佢地唔會失民心<br />\n二黎手足都唔怕出完去發夢番黎仲要驚俾人圍<br />\n<br />\n最後 今晚打人班福建佬<br />\n我地後會有期<br />\n有俾人影到相既你<br />\n希望你有時間著草<br />\n唔係既 我幫你book定上帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e911e904946343e755b107c388ee4c1ba5d32f2","tid":1524042,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:34:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試下找不同？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8480eacf8ab4ac07e30580c7882688f7eedbfa5","tid":1524042,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:34:57.000Z","msg":"推 推到有人回"},{"pid":"c178f4d29204d4dc8aba5dcdd5ffa75efbe83ef7","tid":1524042,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:39:23.000Z","msg":"屌 漏撚左好緊要既一句<br />\n左膠大愛撚死全家"},{"pid":"0e7857b15951f6280e518128232a272cb9e51b7a","tid":1524042,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:39:50.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70seYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=61a4efb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70seYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=08a4ba1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70seYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=ffa457de\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"6a22ea3d49ee8416129f60e8f4071781aae91245","tid":1524042,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:40:21.000Z","msg":"留名加入大西北自衛隊"},{"pid":"093510d5fef372d63877a648373b8def529e041d","tid":1524042,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e78f00c378671ce07514dd26d468c303310e0b5e","tid":1524042,"uid":277671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:41:08.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/a